<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Client Transformations | Caro Creative Co.</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-cream: #FDFBF7;
      --bg-matcha: #F0F5E6;
      --text-charcoal: #0F1115;
      --text-slate: #2F3E32;
      --accent-lime: #B5FF3A;
      --line-soft: rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.10);
      --glass: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.62);
      --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      --font-sans: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 86% 12%, rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.18), transparent 28rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 48%, rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.9), transparent 26rem),
        var(--bg-cream);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3,
    .brand-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-slate);
    }

    .container {
      width: min(100% - 56px, 1240px);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 54px;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-lime {
      background: var(--accent-lime);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.26);
    }

    .btn-lime:hover {
      background: var(--text-charcoal);
      color: var(--bg-cream);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.58);
      border-color: var(--line-soft);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 28px;
      padding: 22px 0;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      min-width: 160px;
    }

    .brand-logo img {
      display: block;
      width: clamp(150px, 15vw, 210px);
      height: auto;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 34px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text-slate);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.04fr) minmax(320px, 0.96fr);
      gap: clamp(38px, 6vw, 84px);
      align-items: center;
      padding: clamp(64px, 8vw, 104px) 0 clamp(52px, 7vw, 88px);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      color: var(--text-slate);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 38px;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-lime);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      max-width: 820px;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 7vw, 6.6rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 690px;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.55vw, 1.16rem);
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 520px;
      border-radius: 64px 170px 64px 64px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 72% 20%, rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.28), transparent 14rem),
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.92), rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.55));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.07);
    }

    .hero-visual::before,
    .hero-visual::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.08);
    }

    .hero-visual::before {
      width: 460px;
      height: 460px;
      left: -190px;
      bottom: -210px;
      background: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.34);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .hero-visual::after {
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      right: -64px;
      top: -74px;
      background: rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.16);
      filter: blur(2px);
    }

    .mockup-stack {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 54px 42px 50px;
      display: grid;
      align-content: center;
      gap: 18px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mockup-card {
      width: min(100%, 420px);
      border-radius: 44px;
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.08);
      padding: 26px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .mockup-card:nth-child(2) {
      justify-self: end;
      width: min(88%, 360px);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .mockup-label {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .mockup-lines {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mockup-lines span {
      display: block;
      height: 13px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(47, 62, 50, 0.10);
    }

    .mockup-lines span:nth-child(1) { width: 86%; }
    .mockup-lines span:nth-child(2) { width: 62%; }
    .mockup-lines span:nth-child(3) { width: 74%; background: rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.62); }

    .section {
      padding: clamp(56px, 7vw, 92px) 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.75fr 1.25fr;
      gap: 42px;
      align-items: end;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }

    .section-heading h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .section-heading p {
      max-width: 680px;
      justify-self: end;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .story-grid {
      column-count: 2;
      column-gap: 32px;
    }

    .story-card {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100%;
      break-inside: avoid;
      margin: 0 0 32px;
      border-radius: 54px;
      background: rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      transition: transform 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease;
    }

    .story-card:nth-child(even) {
      margin-top: 54px;
      background: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.68);
    }

    .story-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.06);
    }

    .story-summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .story-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }

    .story-top {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 250px;
      padding: 34px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.32), transparent 12rem),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.66), rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.92));
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      align-content: space-between;
      gap: 34px;
    }

    .story-top::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: -38px;
      bottom: -58px;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 48px 120px 48px 48px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.08);
      background: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.34);
      transform: rotate(-10deg);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .story-number {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-lime);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .story-client {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text-slate);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .story-pill {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      width: fit-content;
      max-width: 92%;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.44);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.08);
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .story-top h3 {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 430px;
      font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .expand-indicator {
      position: absolute;
      right: 28px;
      top: 28px;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .expand-indicator::before,
    .expand-indicator::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      width: 16px;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--text-charcoal);
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .expand-indicator::after {
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(90deg);
    }

    .story-card[open] .expand-indicator::after {
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg);
    }

    .story-body {
      padding: 34px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 26px;
      animation: revealStory 0.28s ease;
    }

    @keyframes revealStory {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-6px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .story-section {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    }

    .story-section:first-child {
      padding-top: 0;
      border-top: 0;
    }

    .story-section h4 {
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .story-section p {
      font-size: 0.97rem;
    }

    .system-audit {
      border-radius: 58px;
      background: rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.06);
      padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 54px);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .system-audit::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      right: -68px;
      top: -80px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(181, 255, 58, 0.18);
      filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .audit-header {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .audit-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.2vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .audit-header p {
      max-width: 470px;
    }

    table {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    th,
    td {
      padding: 22px 18px;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.10);
    }

    th {
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    td {
      color: var(--text-slate);
    }

    td:first-child {
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .after {
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .faq {
      max-width: 880px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .faq h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.8vw, 4.4rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .faq details {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      padding: 24px 0;
    }

    .faq summary {
      position: relative;
      padding-right: 44px;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      color: var(--text-charcoal);
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.7vw, 1.26rem);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .faq summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq summary::after {
      content: "+";
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: 0;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(240, 245, 230, 0.9);
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .faq details[open] summary::after {
      content: "−";
      background: var(--accent-lime);
    }

    .faq details p {
      max-width: 730px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .footer-wrap {
      padding: 34px 0 38px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
      align-items: start;
      color: var(--text-slate);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .footer-wrap div:last-child {
      text-align: right;
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .container {
        width: min(100% - 36px, 1240px);
      }

      header {
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav ul {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero,
      .section-heading,
      .audit-header {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 48px;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        min-height: 420px;
        border-radius: 52px 120px 52px 52px;
      }

      .section-heading p {
        justify-self: start;
      }

      .story-grid {
        column-count: 1;
      }

      .story-card:nth-child(even) {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .table-scroll {
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding-bottom: 8px;
      }

      table {
        min-width: 720px;
      }

      .footer-wrap {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .footer-wrap div:last-child {
        text-align: left;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      header .btn {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        min-height: 360px;
      }

      .mockup-stack {
        inset: 34px 22px;
      }

      .mockup-card {
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 38px;
      }

      .story-top,
      .story-body {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .story-card,
      .system-audit {
        border-radius: 44px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href="index.html" class="brand-logo" aria-label="Caro Creative Co. home">
        <img src="caro-logo.png" alt="Caro Creative Co.">
      </a>

      <nav aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="index.html">System Architecture</a></li>
          <li><a href="#stories">Client Transformations</a></li>
          <li><a href="#audit">The System Audit</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <a href="#audit" class="btn btn-lime">Request System Audit</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Client Transformations</span>
          <h1>Proven Infrastructure: Client Transformations.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">Caro Creative Co. transforms chaotic operational bottlenecks into systemized brand infrastructure. Read how scaling founders and organizations have reclaimed their time through our signature audit and engineering frameworks.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#stories" class="btn btn-lime">Read the Transformations</a>
            <a href="#audit" class="btn btn-ghost">View the Audit Framework</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="mockup-stack">
            <div class="mockup-card">
              <div class="mockup-label"><span>Audit Map</span><span>01</span></div>
              <div class="mockup-lines">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mockup-card">
              <div class="mockup-label"><span>Delivery System</span><span>Live</span></div>
              <div class="mockup-lines">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="stories">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>From bottleneck to brand engine.</h2>
          <p>Each engagement begins with a diagnostic lens: where is time being lost, what assets are missing, and which communication systems need to become repeatable before the brand can scale gracefully? Expand each story to review the bottleneck, intervention, and result across nine validated system builds.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-grid">
          <details class="story-card" open>
            <summary class="story-summary">
              <div class="story-top">
                <span class="story-number">01</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="story-client">BeInspired Coaching</p>
                  <span class="story-pill">Brand footprint / professionalization</span>
                  <h3>DEI Coaching Practice.</h3>
                </div>
                <span class="expand-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </div>
            </summary>

            <div class="story-body">
              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>Operational Bottleneck</h4>
                <p>A solo DEI coaching practice experiencing rapid scale—growing from one coach to a team of ten in two years—lacked the foundational digital infrastructure to support its expanded capacity. The firm operated with only a logo, leaving them without a digital footprint or a professional landing spot for enterprise-level prospects.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>System Intervention</h4>
                <p>Engineered a scalable brand identity and digital presence. This included developing a cohesive visual language around the existing logo, designing a clean, professional website architecture to house service information, and establishing a professional digital footprint that aligns with the firm’s expanded team and service capacity.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>Result</h4>
                <p>Provided the firm with a unified digital authority, enabling them to transition from a word-of-mouth solo practice to a professionally branded DEI coaching organization capable of capturing and managing high-value client interest.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="story-card">
            <summary class="story-summary">
              <div class="story-top">
                <span class="story-number">02</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="story-client">Every Child Fed</p>
                  <span class="story-pill">Integrated donation / CMS management</span>
                  <h3>Non-Profit Organization.</h3>
                </div>
                <span class="expand-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </div>
            </summary>

            <div class="story-body">
              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>Operational Bottleneck</h4>
                <p>The organization was hindered by a technical platform—a legacy two-page WordPress site—that their internal team could not manage. This created a recurring technical bottleneck that prevented consistent blogging, limited donor communication, and hindered the organization’s ability to drive traffic to their mission.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>System Intervention</h4>
                <p>Engineered a high-performance Squarespace architecture that prioritized team-led administration. The system included a frictionless, integrated donation platform, a simplified editorial interface for consistent content publishing, and an automated newsletter subscription engine that unified donor engagement.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="story-section">
                <h4>Result</h4>
                <p>Transformed an inaccessible technical liability into a scalable, donor-facing communication engine. The organization now manages its own digital presence and maintains consistent donor relations without requiring external technical support.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="story-card">
            <summary class="story-summary">
              <div class="story-top">
                <span class="story-number">03</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="story-client">Catalyst Consulting</p>
                  <span class="story-pill">Lead capture systems / automated funnels</span>
                  <h3>Business Coaching.</h3>
                </div>
                <span class="expand-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></span>
